        "authentication improves scalability, but token revocation is more complex because a token may remain valid "
        "until its expiry time."
    )
    add_section_heading(doc, "5.2 Scalability Finding", 2)
    doc.add_paragraph(
        "In a single-server or centralized application, session storage is manageable. In a distributed deployment, "
